{"tid":1870434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下下要手足用命去make noise 自覺啦好冇？","createTime":"2020-02-08T20:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T08:38:19.000Z","uid":335921,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7928de581833ea3e9bc69bcfb0afe6c84775939d","tid":1870434,"uid":335921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T20:34:50.000Z","msg":"見到有post話多謝手足開花點燃返場運動<br />\n<br />\n個post多謝冇問題<br />\n<br />\n咁大家多謝完諗住下一步係咩？繼續如常生活？<br />\n<br />\n好心啦<br />\n<br />\n成場運動唔係靠手足上街打交開花就夠<br />\n<br />\n群眾運動需要嘅係群眾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">下下靠手足用命去make noise令香港人記得自己仲抗爭緊<br />\n<br />\n仲有幾多手足可以咁犧牲自己？<br />\n<br />\n係咪永遠要踩住其他人嘅屍去爭取你憐憫？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">我好希望，有一日唔再需要手足同我出街搵命搏<br />\n<br />\n好希望香港人能夠善用工會罷工 不合作運動 罷交稅 遊行集會<br />\n<br />\n唔會再有手足要係天上等煲底團聚</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">請未入工會嘅你，依家即刻加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩手機嘅你，去TvB廣告商洗板<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有隊友嘅你出街貼文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭緊車嘅你air drop文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日諗下離開咗我地嘅人<br />\n諗下自己有冇為大家行出個一小步</span>"},{"pid":"460ce3585af9254cbb1ae6c25cc9cd430b6b214f","tid":1870434,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T20:36:08.000Z","msg":"咪有人推靜靜地 但又有人嫌運動冷卻"},{"pid":"daf223b65c17a2683543956acc41bbabd6ab945a","tid":1870434,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T20:36:41.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好用命去搏"},{"pid":"d0e0bded08a1cdfade971e76040918206ed8b6ca","tid":1870434,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T20:37:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d5a97c7a897ade1b71d89e65bda83a291e570eed","tid":1870434,"uid":103890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T20:37:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid"